{"tid":1741542,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[集思廣益]關於黃色經濟圈嘅意見","createTime":"2019-11-20T11:29:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T16:16:11.000Z","uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"17bfda6006d1c729d9088c06e4b6271ea2926a5e","tid":1741542,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T11:29:38.000Z","msg":"表面上，睇post見黃色經濟圈好蓬勃<br />\n實質只係偏向飲食<br />\n但對於其他行業卻冇好好支持<br />\n<strong>我建議，各行各業都有個list</strong><br />\n甚至將其他行業藍店都加入去再加以抵制<br />\n咁樣可以鞏固同埋擴大黃色經濟圈，甚至將香港經濟結構扭轉<br />\n呈現國退民進嘅境象<br />\n我喺呢度就想講下攝影圈<br />\n以我所知就有Justin Law，田老爺同埋Wing Liu呢幾位<br />\n有d甚至講到明唔做警犬生意<br />\n唔知大家點睇"},{"pid":"fc82cd69072827a4ebe252ef42a5d055c877fabc","tid":1741542,"uid":287329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T11:59:54.000Z","msg":"黃的士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c65a0d923f48ec9477184aa20a553f52673d91e","tid":1741542,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T16:16:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}